Package: GCBS
Title: Easy, Reproducible Statistical Analysis and Data Cleaning Tools for Research
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Akash", "Agrawal", email = "your.email@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
  Provides robust, beginner-friendly functions for data cleaning and comprehensive statistical analysis, 
  tailored to the needs of scientific research. Includes easy handling for missing data and recoding, 
  as well as one-line automatic t-tests, ANOVA, linear, logistic, and multinomial regression with 
  stepwise model selection, high-quality plots, cross-validation, model diagnostics, and reproducible 
  report outputs.
